        </p>
        <div class="social-icons">
            <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/sa%C3%A2d-loucifi-83921727a/" target="_blank"><i class="fab fa-linkedin"></i></a>
            <a href="https://www.instagram.com/saad.lcf/" target="_blank"><i class="fab fa-instagram"></i></a>
            <a href="https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=100007577568522" target="_blank"><i class="fab fa-facebook"></i></a>
